ing: 2 (16 ounce) packages smoked turkey sausage, thinly sliced
1 large head cabbage, sliced into strips
salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste
n: Cabbage Stir-Fry with Smoked Turkey Sausage
des: "Just a small amount of ingredients, but you will be shocked at the amount of flavor in this dish!"
ins: Heat a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add sausage; saute until lightly browned, about 3 minutes. Add onion and garlic; saute until the onion has softened and turned translucent, about 5 minutes. Add cabbages season with salt and pepper. Cook and stir until cabbage is translucent and limp, 6 to 10 minutes.
